modules.description: This module detects the tempo of audio data in beats per minute (BPM). It processes audio samples provided either as a Bigarray or as a nested float array, analyzing them to estimate rhythmic patterns. It is used in music analysis applications such as DJ tools or automatic playlist generators where tempo matching is required.

This module processes audio data to adjust tempo, pitch, or playback rate using a provided sample rate and channel count. It accepts interleaved or non-interleaved audio samples for processing and provides access to the transformed output samples. It is used in audio applications like music players, DJ software, or audio editors where real-time sound manipulation is required.
